  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2018-01-11T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Restraining Excessive Federal Enforcement & Regulations of Cannabis Act of 2018 or the REFER Act of 2018\n\nThis bill prohibits the use of funds made available by Congress to a federal department or agency:\n\n to restrict a state or local law that authorizes the use, distribution, possession, or cultivation of cannabis; to detain, prosecute, sentence, or initiate civil proceedings against an individual, business, or property involved in cannabis-related activities in accordance with state or local law; or to penalize a financial institution for providing financial services to a business engaged in cannabis-related activities in compliance with state or local law."
  }, 
